Multiplex presentations with Speaker Notes

Created with : https://github.com/hakimel/reveal.js/


#h1 Installation : 

Add dependencies 



#h2 Server : 

#h3 socket.io
Run socket.io multiplexing :
	- node plugin/multiplex
	
	
Generate token : http://socketio-server:1948/token

Copy and paste id + secret into your index.html server
Specify socket.io server url

#h2 Client : 

Copy and paste id into your index.html client
Specify socket.io server url

Serve static files on your needs : 

server (default port 8080) :
static


client :
static -p 8081


#h1 Using Server Side Speaker Notes

Same manipulations instead of serving your master presentation

Running : node plugin/notes-server into your master directory will run a socket.io server for notes purposes, and serves your master presentation

You can then access your master presentation here : localhost:1947 (default port)

To open your notes, open the JS console and click on the link displayed


