Technique


ReverseProxy
-> /client -> 8081
-> /admin -> 1947


 sudo a2enmod proxy

$ sudo a2enmod proxy_http

restart apache

ServerName presentations.ippon...
ProxyPreserveHost On
ProxyRequests off
ProxyPass /client http://presentations.ippon...:8081
ProxyPassReverse /client http://presentations.ippon...:8081


 Redirect permanent / http://florianlopes.eu:8083/icescrum
        ProxyRequests Off
        ProxyPreserveHost On
        ProxyStatus On
        ProxyPass /* http://florianlopes.eu:8083/icescrum
        ProxyPassReverse /* http://florianlopes.eu:8083/icescrum



